    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not-assessed per MRL 2 scoping, which is consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements for a Class II device at this risk level. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support the COU decision of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met across all 5 operating points with adequate validation evidence.",
